jcsp.net

Class NetChannelEnd

  • java.lang.Object
    • jcsp.net.NetChannelEnd

  • public class NetChannelEnd
extends java.lang.Object

    This class provides static factory methods for constructing Networked channel ends.

    The methods are equivalent to the methods defined in NetChannelEndFactory.
